results.application_description:
Use this application to analyze the skins overall condition.
This app will check the selfies image quality and assess visual skin features, such as:
  1. perceived age
  2. eye age
  3. skin tone
  4. eye bags
  5. uniformness
  6. redness
  7. wrinkles (deprecated)
  8. pores
  9. sagging (deprecated)
  10. acne
  11. pigmentation
  12. translucency
  13. hydration
  14. facial landmarks
  15. lines
For the calculated metrics, the application will produce analytics, which is available in the interface. You can use this application to compare subjects, track skin dynamics over time, and get skin metric reports.
